,"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/3640"},"text":"106 Stat. 3640","children":[],"tail":", which required the Secretary of Veterans Affairs to consider the views and recommendations, if any, of the Advisory Committee on Native-American Veterans in carrying out the direct housing loan pilot program, was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/233/tI/s103/c/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–233, title I, § 103(c)(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2006-06-15"},"text":"June 15, 2006","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/120/400"},"text":"120 Stat. 400","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"idc3b3ab2b-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Annual Reports on Pilot Program","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/547/s8/d"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–547, § 8(d)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/3640"},"text":"106 Stat. 3640","children":[],"tail":", directed Secretary of Veterans Affairs to transmit report relating to implementation of Native American veterans direct housing loan pilot program established under this subchapter to Committees on Veterans’ Affairs of Senate and House of Representatives not later than Feb. 1 of each of years 1994 through 1998, prior to repeal by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/110/tII/s201/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–110, title II, § 201(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-02-13"},"text":"Feb. 13, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/770"},"text":"110 Stat. 770","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"idc3b3ab2c-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Authorization of Appropriations for Native American Veteran Housing Loans","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/547/s8/e"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–547, § 8(e)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/3640"},"text":"106 Stat. 3640","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/102/547/s8/e"},"text":"“New direct loan obligations for Native American veteran housing loans under subchapter V of chapter 37 of title 38, United States Code (as added by subsection (a)), may be incurred only to the extent that appropriations of budget authority to cover the anticipated cost, as defined in section 502 of the Congressional Budget Act of 1974 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t2/s661a"},"text":"2 U.S.C. 661a","children":[],"tail":"], for such loans are made in advance. There is authorized to be appropriated for such purpose $5,000,000 for fiscal year 1993, which amount shall remain available without fiscal year limitation.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
